3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses collaboration and grouping of users, which is a social network concept. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses strategies to improve the capacity of MIMO channels, which is a topic related to multimedia communication. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses strategies to control interference in MIMO channels, which is a topic related to systems and control.
